Koh Ngai ( Ngai Island ) üå¥ Located in Lanta Archipelago Nation Marine Park, Krabi Province. Krabi is great for Nature lovers, especially those who are also fans of sea, sun and sand holidays. Koh Ngai has plenty of beaches, big and small that enjoy gorgeous views of tiny karst islands and some equally well-known nearby islands including Koh Libong and Koh Mook in Trang Province.
